{"title":"Ubuntu命令","date":"2023-02-13T08:11:54.000Z","date_formatted":{"ll":"2023年2月13日","L":"2023/02/13","MM-DD":"02-13"},"thumbnail":"https://picsum.photos/1280/720?random=13","color":"#111","link":"2023/02/13/Ubuntu命令","tags":["💖分享","📔笔记"],"updated":"2023-02-13T08:13:40.039Z","content":"<h2 id=\"system-limit-for-number-of-file-watchers-reached\">System limit for number of file watchers reached<a title=\"#system-limit-for-number-of-file-watchers-reached\" href=\"#system-limit-for-number-of-file-watchers-reached\"></a></h2>\n<p>解决：</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight plaintext\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">echo fs.inotify.max_user_watches=524288 | sudo tee -a /etc/sysctl.conf &amp;&amp; sudo sysctl -p</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<h2 id=\"修改目录权限\">修改目录权限<a title=\"#修改目录权限\" href=\"#修改目录权限\"></a></h2>\n<figure class=\"highlight plaintext\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br><span class=\"line\">4</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1.更改目录所有者命令:</span><br><span class=\"line\">chown -R 用户名称 目录名称</span><br><span class=\"line\">2.更改目录权限命令:</span><br><span class=\"line\">chmod -R 755 目录名称</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<h2 id=\"apt-get代理设置\">apt-get代理设置<a title=\"#apt-get代理设置\" href=\"#apt-get代理设置\"></a></h2>\n<figure class=\"highlight plaintext\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\"># /etc/apt/apt.conf</span><br><span class=\"line\">Acquire::http::proxy &quot;http://username:password@ip:port/&quot;;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<h2 id=\"设置bash代理\">设置bash代理<a title=\"#设置bash代理\" href=\"#设置bash代理\"></a></h2>\n<figure class=\"highlight plaintext\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\"># ~/.bashrc</span><br><span class=\"line\">export HTTP_PROXY=http://username:password@ip:port</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<h2 id=\"更新系统\">更新系统<a title=\"#更新系统\" href=\"#更新系统\"></a></h2>\n<figure class=\"highlight plaintext\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">yum update -y</span><br><span class=\"line\"># /var没有空间可以更改/etc/yum.conf文件下的缓存目录</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<h2 id=\"防火墙开启/关闭端口\">防火墙开启/关闭端口<a title=\"#防火墙开启/关闭端口\" href=\"#防火墙开启/关闭端口\"></a></h2>\n<figure class=\"highlight plaintext\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br><span class=\"line\">4</span><br><span class=\"line\">5</span><br><span class=\"line\">6</span><br><span class=\"line\">7</span><br><span class=\"line\">8</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\"># 关闭端口号</span><br><span class=\"line\">iptables -A OUTPUT -p tcp --dport 端口号-j DROP</span><br><span class=\"line\"># 开启端口号</span><br><span class=\"line\">iptables -A INPUT -ptcp --dport  端口号-j ACCEPT</span><br><span class=\"line\"># 保存</span><br><span class=\"line\">service iptables save</span><br><span class=\"line\"># 查看端口状态</span><br><span class=\"line\">netstat -tunlp</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<h2 id=\"tree命令\">tree命令<a title=\"#tree命令\" href=\"#tree命令\"></a></h2>\n<figure class=\"highlight plaintext\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br><span class=\"line\">4</span><br><span class=\"line\">5</span><br><span class=\"line\">6</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\"># 以树形结果输出目录</span><br><span class=\"line\"># -d 只显示目录</span><br><span class=\"line\"># -L Level 限制深度层级</span><br><span class=\"line\"># -I file 需要忽略的文件</span><br><span class=\"line\"># &gt; file 输出到文件</span><br><span class=\"line\">tree -d -L 3 -I &quot;node_modules|.git|dist|&quot; &gt; ./tree.txt</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<h2 id=\"删除匹配文件\">删除匹配文件<a title=\"#删除匹配文件\" href=\"#删除匹配文件\"></a></h2>\n<figure class=\"highlight plaintext\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">sudo rm $(find ./ -name &#x27;10.124.131*&#x27;)</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<h2 id=\"查看占用端口\">查看占用端口<a title=\"#查看占用端口\" href=\"#查看占用端口\"></a></h2>\n<figure class=\"highlight plaintext\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">netstat -anp | grep 8000</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<h2 id=\"设定有线无线网络共用\">设定有线无线网络共用<a title=\"#设定有线无线网络共用\" href=\"#设定有线无线网络共用\"></a></h2>\n<figure class=\"highlight plaintext\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">route -n</span><br><span class=\"line\">sudo route add default gw 192.168.43.1</span><br><span class=\"line\">sudo route add -net 10.0.0.0 netmask 255.0.0.0 gw 10.161.8.1 dev enp2s0</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<h2 id=\"更新蓝牙驱动\">更新蓝牙驱动<a title=\"#更新蓝牙驱动\" href=\"#更新蓝牙驱动\"></a></h2>\n<figure class=\"highlight plaintext\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">sudo apt install bluetooth blueman</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<h2 id=\"禁止/启用中键粘贴\">禁止/启用中键粘贴<a title=\"#禁止/启用中键粘贴\" href=\"#禁止/启用中键粘贴\"></a></h2>\n<figure class=\"highlight plaintext\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br><span class=\"line\">4</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\"># 禁止</span><br><span class=\"line\">xmodmap -e &quot;pointer = 1 25 3 4 5 6 7 8&quot;</span><br><span class=\"line\"># 启用</span><br><span class=\"line\">xmodmap -e &quot;pointer = 1 2 3 4 5 6 7 8&quot;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<h2 id=\"重启网络服务\">重启网络服务<a title=\"#重启网络服务\" href=\"#重启网络服务\"></a></h2>\n<figure class=\"highlight plaintext\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">sudo service network-manager restart</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<h2 id=\"修改本地时区\">修改本地时区<a title=\"#修改本地时区\" href=\"#修改本地时区\"></a></h2>\n<figure class=\"highlight plaintext\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">sudo timedatectl set-timezone Asia/Shanghai</span><br><span class=\"line\">sudo timedatectl set-local-rtc 1</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n","prev":{"title":"Nginx配置","link":"2023/02/13/Nginx配置"},"next":{"title":"Canvas拖拽和缩放","link":"2023/02/13/Canvas拖拽和缩放"},"plink":"https://fenglekai.github.io/2023/02/13/Ubuntu命令/","toc":[{"id":"system-limit-for-number-of-file-watchers-reached","title":"System limit for number of file watchers reached","index":"1"},{"id":"修改目录权限","title":"修改目录权限","index":"2"},{"id":"apt-get代理设置","title":"apt-get代理设置","index":"3"},{"id":"设置bash代理","title":"设置bash代理","index":"4"},{"id":"更新系统","title":"更新系统","index":"5"},{"id":"防火墙开启/关闭端口","title":"防火墙开启&#x2F;关闭端口","index":"6"},{"id":"tree命令","title":"tree命令","index":"7"},{"id":"删除匹配文件","title":"删除匹配文件","index":"8"},{"id":"查看占用端口","title":"查看占用端口","index":"9"},{"id":"设定有线无线网络共用","title":"设定有线无线网络共用","index":"10"},{"id":"更新蓝牙驱动","title":"更新蓝牙驱动","index":"11"},{"id":"禁止/启用中键粘贴","title":"禁止&#x2F;启用中键粘贴","index":"12"},{"id":"重启网络服务","title":"重启网络服务","index":"13"},{"id":"修改本地时区","title":"修改本地时区","index":"14"}],"reading_time":"404 字约 3 分钟"}